Watch out.

5
00:01:45,320 --> 00:01:46,360
Morning, Uncle Long.

6
00:01:46,360 --> 00:01:48,200
Pay the rent. Hurry up.

7
00:01:48,200 --> 00:01:50,320
- Drinking?
- Collecting rent!

8
00:01:50,320 --> 00:01:52,560
- Chu San, you're back.
- Yeah, I'm back.

9
00:01:53,360 --> 00:01:55,040
You haven't paid yet.

10
00:01:55,040 --> 00:01:57,200
Pay up.

11
00:01:59,410 --> 00:02:01,280
Bastard!

12
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:03,160
Don't run.

13
00:02:03,160 --> 00:02:04,760
Stop right there.

14
00:02:07,440 --> 00:02:09,760
You bastard, I'll chop you to death.

15
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:12,120
My name is He Chu San.

16
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:14,280
I'm a native of Ganglong Walled City.

17
00:02:14,280 --> 00:02:17,520
Ganglong Walled City is
a lawless black zone in Hong Kong.

18
00:02:17,520 --> 00:02:21,400
It's home to the poor,
gamblers, and prostitutes.

19
00:02:21,400 --> 00:02:24,040
Big and small gangs
fight openly and secretly here.

20
00:02:24,040 --> 00:02:27,160
They fight to the death,
with blood and flesh flying.

21
00:02:30,160 --> 00:02:31,480
But there are also many people living here,

22
00:02:31,480 --> 00:02:34,520
ordinary folks surviving amid the violence.

23
00:02:34,520 --> 00:02:37,200
Some of us avoid the underworld at all costs,

24
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:40,880
while others flock to it eagerly.

25
00:02:43,640 --> 00:02:45,000
Fei asked me to give this to you.

26
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:46,440
Thanks.

27
00:02:48,160 --> 00:02:49,720
Uncle Bei, help yourself. It's on us.

28
00:02:49,720 --> 00:02:51,600
Then I won't stand on ceremony.

29
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:53,320
Uncle Bei.

30
00:02:53,320 --> 00:02:54,760
Do you know those guys
who were slashing people just now?

31
00:02:54,760 --> 00:02:56,200
They looked so intimidating.

32
00:02:56,200 --> 00:02:57,240
Of course I know them.

33
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:59,840
They're Xia Liu Yi's men.

34
00:02:59,840 --> 00:03:03,520
The top enforcer in Ganglong Walled City,

35
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:05,720
raised by Qing Long, the boss of Xiaoqi Hall,

36
00:03:05,720 --> 00:03:08,200
and personally trained as his top fighter.

37
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:09,760
Top fighter?

38
00:03:09,760 --> 00:03:14,200
He's the best fighter in all of Xiaoqi Hall.

39
00:03:14,200 --> 00:03:15,360
Six years ago,

40
00:03:15,360 --> 00:03:20,120
to rescue Boss Qing Long, who was surrounded,

41
00:03:20,120 --> 00:03:21,400
he went alone,

42
00:03:21,400 --> 00:03:22,680
wielding two machetes by himself,

43
00:03:22,680 --> 00:03:23,880
and kept slashing,

44
00:03:23,880 --> 00:03:26,120
taking down more than 40 men.

45
00:03:26,120 --> 00:03:29,520
He chased them for three whole blocks.

46
00:03:30,320 --> 00:03:35,680
That battle is known in the underworld
as "Black Children's Day."

47
00:03:39,720 --> 00:03:42,200
From then on, if someone offended him,

48
00:03:42,200 --> 00:03:44,600
he would hold them at blade point

49
00:03:44,600 --> 00:03:47,240
and invite them to celebrate Children's Day.

50
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:49,400
That's not right. Facing 40 enemies...

51
00:03:49,400 --> 00:03:51,240
If each one had a 20 percent chance

52
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:52,760
of successfully striking back at Xia Liu Yi,

53
00:03:52,760 --> 00:03:55,600
then the probability of him
knocking down all of them without injuries

54
00:03:55,600 --> 00:03:58,160
would be 0.8 to the 40th power,

55
00:03:58,160 --> 00:03:59,720
which is approximately...

56
00:04:00,800 --> 00:04:02,160
Uncle Bei.

57
00:04:02,160 --> 00:04:05,200
Even if Xia Liu Yi
has exceptional combat skills

58
00:04:05,200 --> 00:04:06,240
and can knock down 40 people in a row,

59
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:07,600
the possibility of doing so
without being injured

60
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:09,080
is still infinitesimally close to zero.

61
00:04:09,080 --> 00:04:12,280
So, now you're saying I'm old and senile, huh?

62
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:14,560
I was a member of Xiaoqi Hall back then.

63
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:16,380
I saw it with my own eyes.

64
00:04:16,380 --> 00:04:18,800
Even brute force has to
follow the laws of science.

65
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:22,240
And gangsters usually
exaggerate their exploits to show off.

66
00:04:22,240 --> 00:04:25,000
In reality, joining a gang is not only illegal

67
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:26,480
and punishable by law,

68
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:28,000
even in a small-scale brawl,

69
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:30,680
the fatality rate can be as high as 80 percent.

70
00:04:31,320 --> 00:04:34,000
For the two of you,

71
00:04:34,000 --> 00:04:36,320
