he's messed up his brain.

77
00:04:45,840 --> 00:04:48,400
Uncle Bei, you might not believe it,

78
00:04:48,400 --> 00:04:49,840
but I've been reading lately,

79
00:04:49,840 --> 00:04:52,520
and I came across people
who recruit newcomers for gangs

80
00:04:52,520 --> 00:04:54,080
and earn headcount commissions.

81
00:04:54,720 --> 00:04:57,600
You're not making
that kind of money too, are you?

82
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:59,440
