97
00:05:24,840 --> 00:05:28,080
He's the first college student
from Ganglong Walled City.

98
00:05:28,080 --> 00:05:31,160
He got into the University of Hong Kong
with the top score in the whole city.

99
00:05:31,160 --> 00:05:33,360
If he teaches you anything,

100
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:35,960
