152
00:09:31,840 --> 00:09:34,240
Rascal Quan, I finally caught you.

153
00:09:34,240 --> 00:09:36,560
Sorry, I was wrong!

154
00:09:36,560 --> 00:09:37,880
You can't see me, you can't see me...

155
00:09:37,880 --> 00:09:39,280
You can't see me.

156
