241
00:16:28,760 --> 00:16:30,920
Lai Quan is spineless.

242
00:16:30,920 --> 00:16:32,760
He confessed after barely being beaten.

243
00:16:32,760 --> 00:16:35,120
He said his would pay the money.

244
00:16:35,120 --> 00:16:39,560
