254
00:16:59,360 --> 00:17:02,280
Fuck! I get even angrier
when I mention that woman!

255
00:17:02,280 --> 00:17:03,280
I called her,

256
00:17:03,280 --> 00:17:06,185
she said she's cut ties with her brother,

257
00:17:06,185 --> 00:17:07,490
