258
00:17:07,490 --> 00:17:09,340
Damn her!

259
00:17:09,340 --> 00:17:10,720
Bring him here.

260
00:17:11,820 --> 00:17:13,560
Bring him over.

261
00:17:34,520 --> 00:17:35,520
Move.

262
00:17:35,520 --> 00:17:37,720
- Kneel.
- Kneel!

263
00:17:37,720 --> 00:17:39,600
Liu Yi...

264
00:17:39,600 --> 00:17:40,960
My refuses to acknowledge me.

265
00:17:40,960 --> 00:17:42,520
There's nothing I can do.

266
00:17:42,520 --> 00:17:44,160
Liu Yi, I'm begging you! Please let me go!

267
00:17:44,160 --> 00:17:45,800
