268
00:17:45,800 --> 00:17:46,960
No, Liu Yi.

269
00:17:46,960 --> 00:17:48,480
Please let me go.

270
00:17:49,160 --> 00:17:50,880
- Move.
- Move!

271
00:17:56,600 --> 00:17:57,720
Hold him down.

272
00:17:57,720 --> 00:17:59,440
Don't move.

273
00:18:05,680 --> 00:18:07,360
Another one.

274
00:18:30,360 --> 00:18:32,360
Think it over yourself.

275
00:18:32,360 --> 00:18:34,280
One finger.

276
00:18:34,280 --> 00:18:36,720
I'll help you think.

277
00:18:36,720 --> 00:18:38,960
Three fingers.

278
00:18:41,560 --> 00:18:43,600
Liu Yi, I'll go find my mom.

279
00:18:43,600 --> 00:18:45,040
I'll find my mom.

280
00:18:45,040 --> 00:18:46,720
Liu Yi, please spare me.

281
00:18:46,720 --> 00:18:48,400
Please let me go.

282
00:18:48,400 --> 00:18:50,000
One finger.

283
00:18:50,000 --> 00:18:51,360
Liu Yi, no!

284
00:18:51,360 --> 00:18:53,240
No! No, Liu Yi!

285
00:18:53,240 --> 00:18:54,840
No, Liu Yi!

286
00:19:00,600 --> 00:19:02,320
Wrap up the finger.

287
00:19:02,320 --> 00:19:04,080
Send it to Lai San Mei.

288
00:19:04,080 --> 00:19:06,080
Have her pass a message to Fei Qi.

289
00:19:06,080 --> 00:19:07,680
Tonight at ten,

290
00:19:07,680 --> 00:19:13,280
Qing Long will be
at Fengtai Nightclub waiting for him.

291
00:19:18,160 --> 00:19:19,840
- Move!
- Move!

292
00:19:22,640 --> 00:19:24,040
Boss, you caught Lai Quan

293
00:19:24,040 --> 00:19:26,200
just to get to Fei Qi, right?

294
00:19:26,200 --> 00:19:28,600
Are you playing games with me here?

295
00:19:31,280 --> 00:19:33,520
Boss, you're truly wise and brave.

296
00:19:33,520 --> 00:19:34,600
You...

297
00:19:35,360 --> 00:19:36,600
I know this kind of job.

298
00:19:36,600 --> 00:19:38,040
I love doing this.

299
00:19:38,040 --> 00:19:41,000
I'm going crazy staying at that film studio.

300
00:19:41,000 --> 00:19:42,000
If I'm not sending you,

301
00:19:42,000 --> 00:19:44,360
it's because I have
something else for you to do.

302
00:19:47,360 --> 00:19:48,360
Who are we chopping down?

303
00:19:48,360 --> 00:19:49,920
Just say the word.

304
00:20:00,040 --> 00:20:01,720
What...

305
00:20:01,720 --> 00:20:03,120
What did you just say?

306
00:20:03,120 --> 00:20:07,600
I-I majored in finance.

307
00:20:09,280 --> 00:20:10,440
And?

308
00:20:13,800 --> 00:20:15,720
I can write scripts.

309
00:20:17,720 --> 00:20:19,280
Good.

310
00:20:20,600 --> 00:20:21,880
Go home.

311
00:20:26,680 --> 00:20:27,840
Stop.

312
00:20:33,800 --> 00:20:35,440
Take the money.

313
00:20:36,120 --> 00:20:38,320
Work for me

314
00:20:38,320 --> 00:20:39,880
and you'll be well paid.

315
00:20:41,280 --> 00:20:42,880
A hundred thousand.

316
00:20:45,840 --> 00:20:47,320
Dad works ten hours a day at the clinic,

317
00:20:47,320 --> 00:20:48,520
charging 5 yuan per patient.

318
00:20:48,520 --> 00:20:49,760
After deducting the cost of medicine,

319
00:20:49,760 --> 00:20:51,120
his net income is about 40 yuan a day.

320
00:20:51,120 --> 00:20:53,000
That's roughly 14,000 a year.

321
00:20:53,000 --> 00:20:55,880
That means Dad alone, working rain or shine,

322
00:20:55,880 --> 00:20:58,520
would have to slog seven years
to earn this much.

323
00:21:00,480 --> 00:21:02,360
A hundred thousand.

324
00:21:03,560 --> 00:21:04,840
Oh my God.

325
00:21:09,400 --> 00:21:11,400
Chu San, you're back.

326
00:21:12,160 --> 00:21:13,760
By the way, I left food on the table.

327
00:21:13,760 --> 00:21:15,200
Why didn't you eat it?

328
00:21:17,080 --> 00:21:18,680
Dad.

329
00:21:18,680 --> 00:21:21,000
I already ate at Fei's place.

330
00:21:21,840 --> 00:21:24,160
This brat made her spend money again.

331
00:21:24,160 --> 00:21:26,280
That's really embarrassing.

332
00:21:26,280 --> 00:21:27,800
Dad.

333
00:21:31,040 --> 00:21:32,280
Dad, I'm sleepy.

334
00:21:32,280 --> 00:21:34,200
I'm going to bed first.

335
00:21:35,120 --> 00:21:36,120
Okay.

336
00:21:36,120 --> 00:21:37,840
Go to bed early.

337
00:21:37,840 --> 00:21:40,080
You should rest early too, Dad.

338
00:21:40,080 --> 00:21:41,680
All right.

339
00:21:41,680 --> 00:21:43,200
You little brat.

340
00:21:49,520 --> 00:21:50,800
No.

341
00:21:51,480 --> 00:21:53,240
I can't take money from the triads.

342
00:21:53,240 --> 00:21:55,480
It would drag Dad into trouble.

343
00:21:55,480 --> 00:21:56,960
Not to mention Dad said

344
00:21:56,960 --> 00:21:59,560
Mom died because of the triads.

345
00:22:01,080 --> 00:22:03,280
If I take their money,

346
00:22:03,280 --> 00:22:05,920
I'm no different from them.

347
00:22:24,400 --> 00:22:26,480
"One Hundred and One Loves."

348
00:22:32,960 --> 00:22:34,800
They want a script.

349
00:22:35,560 --> 00:22:37,320
Then I'll give them a script.

350
00:22:38,480 --> 00:22:40,280
The rest has nothing to do with me.

351
00:23:04,160 --> 00:23:06,520
Ladies, you're off work.

352
00:23:06,520 --> 00:23:09,200
Liu Yi is hosting an important client tonight.

353
00:23:09,200 --> 00:23:10,800
- Happy now?
- Let's go out and have some fun.

354
00:23:10,800 --> 00:23:12,440
Let's go.

355
00:23:13,400 --> 00:23:15,200
Boss, Fei Qi is here.

356
00:23:15,200 --> 00:23:16,520
Lai San Mei is with him, too.

357
00:23:16,520 --> 00:23:18,480
When will Qing Long arrive?

358
00:23:25,560 --> 00:23:27,760
He went to Thailand.

359
00:23:27,760 --> 00:23:29,880
I'm hosting tonight.

360
00:23:47,520 --> 00:23:48,760
Qi.

361
00:23:48,760 --> 00:23:51,040
I've long heard of your reputation.

362
00:23:58,080 --> 00:24:00,720
Qing Long invited me, and he's late himself.

363
00:24:00,720 --> 00:24:02,465
What's that supposed to mean?

364
00:24:02,465 --> 00:24:04,526
You shithead...

365
00:24:08,480 --> 00:24:09,840
Qi.

366
00:24:09,840 --> 00:24:13,000
Qing Long specially prepared
a performance just for you.

367
00:24:15,600 --> 00:24:20,080
But Uncle Yuan suddenly had a heart attack.

368
00:24:20,080 --> 00:24:23,160
Everyone knows that Qing Long

369
00:24:23,160 --> 00:24:24,960
is closest to Uncle Yuan.

370
00:24:24,960 --> 00:24:27,480
As soon as he found out,
he rushed to the hospital.

371
00:24:27,480 --> 00:24:32,160
But he didn't want you to miss
such a wonderful performance.

372
00:24:32,160 --> 00:24:34,520
So, he asked me to host you here.

373
00:24:35,760 --> 00:24:39,360
Even if Qing Long isn't here,
who do you think you are?

374
00:24:40,560 --> 00:24:43,040
Come on, call them in.

375
00:24:55,880 --> 00:24:57,400
Call them in.

376
00:24:57,400 --> 00:25:00,000
Hello, sir.

377
00:25:09,160 --> 00:25:11,480
Since you're already here,
sit down and have some fun.

378
00:25:11,480 --> 00:25:12,760
All right, fine.

379
00:25:13,840 --> 00:25:14,960
Go on.

380
00:25:37,000 --> 00:25:38,800
Qi.

381
00:25:38,800 --> 00:25:41,480
Our nightclub isn't bad, right?

382
00:25:41,480 --> 00:25:44,800
Then about opening
a noodle stall on your turf...

383
00:25:44,800 --> 00:25:46,200
Qi.

384
00:25:50,640 --> 00:25:51,640
Liu Yi, you're here.

385
00:25:51,640 --> 00:25:53,040
I saw the "Closed" sign outside.

386
00:25:53,040 --> 00:25:54,040
I thought some underlings

387
00:25:54,040 --> 00:25:56,520
were slacking off and having fun on their own.

388
00:25:58,280 --> 00:25:59,560
Xu.

389
00:25:59,560 --> 00:26:00,720
Xu.

390
00:26:04,400 --> 00:26:06,400
Fei Qi is here, too.

391
00:26:09,080 --> 00:26:10,120
Liu Yi.

392
00:26:10,120 --> 00:26:12,640
This is your mistake.

393
00:26:12,640 --> 00:26:14,960
The boss has gone to Thailand.

394
00:26:14,960 --> 00:26:16,800
Qi came to our nightclub.

395
00:26:16,800 --> 00:26:19,400
I should be the one hosting him.

396
00:26:19,400 --> 00:26:21,040
Right, Qi?

397
00:26:21,040 --> 00:26:22,640
What's going on?

398
00:26:24,040 --> 00:26:25,960
Qing Long isn't here.

399
00:26:28,560 --> 00:26:29,880
Xiao Liu.

400
00:26:30,840 --> 00:26:33,000
Are you messing with me?

401
00:26:33,000 --> 00:26:35,200
If Qing Long isn't around,
do you think you can just summon me?

402
00:26:35,200 --> 00:26:36,760
All right, calm down.

403
00:26:36,760 --> 00:26:38,240
This is our turf.

404
00:26:38,240 --> 00:26:40,680
Boss, do we make a move?

405
00:26:41,640 --> 00:26:42,840
Qing Long is here!

406
00:26:42,840 --> 00:26:43,840
- Boss!
- Boss!

407
00:26:43,840 --> 00:26:45,640
- Move, move!
- Boss!

408
00:26:45,640 --> 00:26:47,120
Boss!

409
00:26:47,120 --> 00:26:48,280
Boss!

410
00:27:02,320 --> 00:27:05,560
- Boss.
- Qi, long time no see.

411
00:27:05,560 --> 00:27:07,480
Something urgent came up before I left.

412
00:27:07,480 --> 00:27:09,680
So, I asked my men to keep you company.

413
00:27:09,680 --> 00:27:13,960
You don't think. I was
deliberately slighting you, do you?

414
00:27:15,960 --> 00:27:17,400
Of course not.

415
00:27:17,400 --> 00:27:19,560
Everyone has times they can't get away.

416
00:27:19,560 --> 00:27:21,720
We're brothers, so don't say such things.

417
00:27:21,720 --> 00:27:23,880
It has to be you...

418
00:27:23,880 --> 00:27:26,040
So magnanimous as always.

419
00:27:35,800 --> 00:27:38,040
Unlike me.

420
00:27:38,040 --> 00:27:40,000
I can never gain weight.

421
00:27:47,920 --> 00:27:49,680
Since you're so busy,

422
00:27:49,680 --> 00:27:51,960
I'll keep it brief.

423
00:27:51,960 --> 00:27:54,000
I asked you here today

424
00:27:54,000 --> 00:27:56,560
to discuss the nightclub's matter.

425
00:28:00,480 --> 00:28:03,000
Whatever you say, we'll do.

426
00:28:03,800 --> 00:28:05,000
I heard recently

427
00:28:05,000 --> 00:28:07,640
you got the top batch of goods from Thailand.

428
00:28:07,640 --> 00:28:09,480
I can even make money lying down.

429
00:28:09,480 --> 00:28:12,080
Of course I'm willing.

430
00:28:12,080 --> 00:28:16,760
However, I have a brother-in-law
named Lai Quan.

431
00:28:16,760 --> 00:28:20,160
Liu Yi told me that his men
grabbed the wrong person.

432
00:28:20,160 --> 00:28:22,320
He was so anxious he didn't know what to do.

433
00:28:22,320 --> 00:28:25,400
So, I told him to come in person

434
00:28:25,400 --> 00:28:27,280
to apologize to you.

435
00:28:29,240 --> 00:28:32,680
Qi, my men caught the wrong person.

436
00:28:32,680 --> 00:28:33,960
That's on me.

437
00:28:35,560 --> 00:28:36,960
I'll punish myself with a drink.

438
00:28:47,280 --> 00:28:48,960
It's a small matter.

439
00:28:48,960 --> 00:28:50,560
Nothing worth mentioning.

440
00:28:51,360 --> 00:28:53,720
It matters.

441
00:28:53,720 --> 00:28:55,720
The Hesheng nightclub business...

442
00:28:55,720 --> 00:28:57,880
He'll be in charge of it in the future.

443
00:29:01,760 --> 00:29:04,920
And the moment he shows up, he offends you.

444
00:29:05,840 --> 00:29:07,440
What kind of start is that?

445
00:29:11,520 --> 00:29:12,560
We're all in good spirits today.

446
00:29:12,560 --> 00:29:15,160
Let's not talk about this nonsense, all right?

447
00:29:15,160 --> 00:29:17,080
Liu Yi, pour Qi a drink.

448
00:29:17,080 --> 00:29:18,200
Okay.

449
00:29:18,200 --> 00:29:19,680
Pour it.

450
00:29:19,680 --> 00:29:22,880
Qi, a great man overlooks petty faults.

451
00:29:22,880 --> 00:29:24,480
I raise a toast to you.

452
00:29:24,480 --> 00:29:26,560
I'll finish it.

453
00:29:29,040 --> 00:29:31,840
Qi, it really was a misunderstanding today.

454
00:29:31,840 --> 00:29:33,480
Work hard, buddy.

455
00:29:33,480 --> 00:29:35,680
You've got a bigshot backing you.

456
00:29:35,680 --> 00:29:38,920
Xiao Ma, see Qi out.

457
00:29:38,920 --> 00:29:40,800
Kun, take the brothers to look around.

458
00:29:40,800 --> 00:29:42,360
Let's go.

459
00:29:42,360 --> 00:29:43,680
Okay.

460
00:29:43,680 --> 00:29:44,865
This way.

461
00:29:44,865 --> 00:29:45,897
This way.

462
00:29:45,897 --> 00:29:48,138
Fuck you.

463
00:29:53,840 --> 00:29:55,200
Are you kidding me?

464
00:29:55,200 --> 00:29:57,600
That fatty can really drink.

465
00:29:57,600 --> 00:29:59,880
He drained all my liquor.

466
00:29:59,880 --> 00:30:01,840
Unbelievable.

467
00:30:22,720 --> 00:30:24,000
Big Bro.

468
00:30:26,120 --> 00:30:28,280
Why did you suddenly come back?

469
00:30:29,000 --> 00:30:30,880
Big Bro.

470
00:30:30,880 --> 00:30:33,880
Is this nightclub really for me?

471
00:30:35,000 --> 00:30:37,640
You're not doubting your brother, are you?

472
00:30:37,640 --> 00:30:39,520
When have I ever lied to you?

473
00:30:43,160 --> 00:30:45,600
If I hadn't come back early today,

474
00:30:46,760 --> 00:30:49,040
I'd like to see how you'd have wrapped this up.

475
00:30:49,040 --> 00:30:51,160
Big Bro!

476
00:30:51,160 --> 00:30:56,080
I'm lucky, with you backing me up, right?

477
00:30:56,080 --> 00:30:58,920
Besides, the film studio making movies,

478
00:30:58,920 --> 00:31:00,160
the whole money-laundering thing,

479
00:31:00,160 --> 00:31:04,800
should have been handled by Cui Dong Dong.

480
00:31:04,800 --> 00:31:07,600
Bro, what am I?

481
00:31:07,600 --> 00:31:10,000
A gang enforcer.

482
00:31:10,000 --> 00:31:13,600
I should be the one
charging into battle for you.

483
00:31:13,600 --> 00:31:16,160
All for taking over territories.

484
00:31:16,160 --> 00:31:19,760
I get bored staying in the film studio all day.

485
00:31:20,480 --> 00:31:22,240
Listen.

486
00:31:22,240 --> 00:31:24,760
Although the nightclub is yours,

487
00:31:24,760 --> 00:31:27,880
the film studio is your primary responsibility.

488
00:31:27,880 --> 00:31:29,400
One month.

489
00:31:29,400 --> 00:31:30,960
I'll give you a month.

490
00:31:30,960 --> 00:31:32,600
Get the movie done.

491
00:31:32,600 --> 00:31:34,280
Oversee it personally.

492
00:31:34,280 --> 00:31:35,880
Also, spend some time with Xiao Man.

493
00:31:35,880 --> 00:31:37,600
No, bro!

494
00:31:37,600 --> 00:31:40,240
The studio is really boring.

495
00:31:40,240 --> 00:31:43,360
Every time I'm in the studio, I feel like...

496
00:31:43,360 --> 00:31:44,440
Big Bro!

497
00:31:46,160 --> 00:31:47,920
Bro, are you okay?

498
00:31:53,200 --> 00:31:54,520
I'm fine.

499
00:31:54,520 --> 00:31:55,920
I've just been too busy.

500
00:31:55,920 --> 00:31:57,760
Just a little tired.

501
00:31:57,760 --> 00:31:59,000
You've worked hard.

502
00:31:59,000 --> 00:32:00,480
Thanks, bro.

503
00:32:16,360 --> 00:32:18,360
I just want what's best for you, too.

504
00:32:23,200 --> 00:32:25,280
I've told you many times.

505
00:32:25,280 --> 00:32:28,080
Always tie your tie properly
when wearing a suit.

506
00:32:28,080 --> 00:32:30,040
You never listen.

507
00:32:30,040 --> 00:32:32,000
You rebellious kid.

508
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:33,280
I'm leaving.

509
00:32:35,960 --> 00:32:37,960
Bro, get some rest.

510
00:32:37,960 --> 00:32:39,280
Goodbye.

511
00:32:47,200 --> 00:32:50,680
Boss, do we still have to
go back to the film studio?

512
00:32:50,680 --> 00:32:52,840
Are you stupid?

513
00:32:52,840 --> 00:32:54,400
The movie must be made.

514
00:32:54,400 --> 00:32:56,680
This is our big brother's order.

515
00:32:56,680 --> 00:32:57,960
But...

516
00:32:58,800 --> 00:33:00,720
With the director you found...

517
00:33:00,720 --> 00:33:03,440
Can he finish filming in a month?

518
00:33:05,000 --> 00:33:06,120
What does he do?

519
00:33:06,120 --> 00:33:08,480
Has he won the Oscars or awards?

520
00:33:12,920 --> 00:33:14,240
Got it!

521
00:33:14,240 --> 00:33:17,880
We only need ten days to make the movie.

522
00:33:17,880 --> 00:33:21,120
The rest of the time,

523
00:33:21,120 --> 00:33:25,680
we can come to the nightclub
and continue partying.

524
00:33:25,680 --> 00:33:27,400
Do you want to die?

525
00:33:27,400 --> 00:33:29,760
- Boss!
- I'll kick you into your grave!

526
00:33:29,760 --> 00:33:31,800
- Don't run!
- Boss!

527
00:33:40,040 --> 00:33:41,520
Hao Cheng Qing.

528
00:33:41,520 --> 00:33:43,160
For a pretty boy,

529
00:33:43,160 --> 00:33:44,120
you've trampled on me,

530
00:33:44,120 --> 00:33:46,520
your buddy who's been with you
through thick and thin.

531
00:33:56,600 --> 00:33:59,960
♪ The midnight bell just rang ♪

532
00:33:59,960 --> 00:34:03,280
♪ The neon lights are flickering ♪

533
00:34:03,280 --> 00:34:06,880
♪ Who's seeking escape in a drink? ♪

534
00:34:06,880 --> 00:34:10,320
♪ Who's causing trouble on the dance floor? ♪

535
00:34:11,140 --> 00:34:14,880
♪ When the music plays, don't think too much ♪

536
00:34:14,880 --> 00:34:18,180
♪ Your body starts moving uncontrollably ♪

537
00:34:18,180 --> 00:34:20,480
♪ All your troubles are drowned out ♪

538
00:34:20,480 --> 00:34:22,920
♪ Follow the rhythm, dance like crazy ♪

539
00:34:22,920 --> 00:34:25,280
Awesome. You're awesome.

540
00:34:25,280 --> 00:34:26,480
I'm not going to the nightclub.

541
00:34:26,480 --> 00:34:27,920
I'm not going.

542
00:34:27,920 --> 00:34:30,620
Let go of me, let go!

543
00:34:30,620 --> 00:34:35,520
♪ Who cares about tomorrow at this moment? ♪

544
00:34:35,520 --> 00:34:37,480
Boss.

545
00:34:37,480 --> 00:34:38,640
Boss!

546
00:34:39,960 --> 00:34:41,480
I brought this guy.

547
00:34:41,480 --> 00:34:42,600
Any other orders?

548
00:34:42,600 --> 00:34:43,840
Go have fun.

549
00:34:43,840 --> 00:34:45,040
All right.

550
00:34:45,040 --> 00:34:46,180
I'm here.

551
00:34:46,180 --> 00:34:47,460
Let's have fun!

552
00:34:54,920 --> 00:34:56,400
College student.

553
00:34:56,400 --> 00:34:57,400
It's been three days.

554
00:34:57,400 --> 00:34:59,000
Where's the script?

555
00:35:22,960 --> 00:35:24,200
The Little Mermaid.

556
00:35:24,200 --> 00:35:27,400
To see the human prince again,

557
00:35:28,880 --> 00:35:31,920
she made a deal with the sea witch.

558
00:35:31,920 --> 00:35:35,280
She painfully gave up her tail.

559
00:35:41,280 --> 00:35:42,480
Fin.

560
00:35:44,960 --> 00:35:46,200
You read.

561
00:35:51,640 --> 00:35:53,960
She traded it for legs to walk on land.

562
00:35:53,960 --> 00:35:55,160
When she stepped onto land,

563
00:35:55,160 --> 00:35:56,360
every step felt like being cut by a knife.

564
00:35:56,360 --> 00:35:58,120
Speak louder.

565
00:35:59,160 --> 00:36:02,240
She still hoped to find the prince.

566
00:36:02,240 --> 00:36:06,320
But she didn't know
the shadow over this port city

567
00:36:06,320 --> 00:36:11,160
was ruled by a terrifying
dual-blade mafia boss.

568
00:36:11,160 --> 00:36:14,560
The mafia boss controls
the city's underground dealings.

569
00:36:16,920 --> 00:36:19,800
This boss also wields dual blades?

570
00:36:21,760 --> 00:36:23,800
Isn't that impressive?

571
00:36:42,200 --> 00:36:44,200
Why hide it?

572
00:36:44,960 --> 00:36:47,080
Stop being sneaky with me.

573
00:36:47,080 --> 00:36:49,520
Scheming behind my back.

574
00:36:49,520 --> 00:36:51,040
College student.

575
00:36:51,040 --> 00:36:53,720
Money isn't made this way.

576
00:36:53,720 --> 00:36:55,480
Rewrite it.

577
00:36:55,480 --> 00:36:57,360
- Got it.
- Now.

578
00:37:10,200 --> 00:37:13,400
♪ The midnight bell just rang ♪

579
00:37:13,400 --> 00:37:15,280
♪ The neon lights are flickering ♪

580
00:37:15,280 --> 00:37:17,840
I'm studying finance.
I don't know how to write scripts.

581
00:37:17,840 --> 00:37:20,080
♪ Who's seeking escape in a drink? ♪

582
00:37:20,080 --> 00:37:24,640
♪ Who's causing trouble on the dance floor? ♪

583
00:37:24,640 --> 00:37:28,280
♪ When the music plays, don't think too much ♪

584
00:37:28,280 --> 00:37:31,440
♪ Your body starts moving uncontrollably ♪

585
00:37:31,440 --> 00:37:34,240
♪ All your troubles are drowned out ♪

586
00:37:34,240 --> 00:37:36,880
♪ Follow the rhythm, dance like crazy ♪

587
00:37:36,880 --> 00:37:39,000
♪ Your heartbeat's about to explode ♪

588
00:37:39,000 --> 00:37:41,360
♪ The alcohol burns it away ♪

589
00:37:41,360 --> 00:37:47,920
♪ Who cares about tomorrow at this moment? ♪

590
00:38:58,400 --> 00:38:59,600
Freaking hell.

591
00:38:59,600 --> 00:39:01,400
Who is it?

592
00:39:03,320 --> 00:39:04,600
Boss!

593
00:39:07,280 --> 00:39:08,520
Boss!

594
00:39:09,320 --> 00:39:11,680
Qing Long is going
to the film studio to check in.

595
00:39:11,680 --> 00:39:12,760
His wife is coming, too.

596
00:39:12,760 --> 00:39:14,480
She's already on the way.

597
00:39:15,480 --> 00:39:16,960
Hurry, wake them up.

598
00:39:17,800 --> 00:39:19,240
Get up!

599
00:39:19,240 --> 00:39:20,760
Get up!

600
00:39:20,760 --> 00:39:22,960
- Back to the studio.
- I have class.

601
00:39:22,960 --> 00:39:24,120
Let's go. Ten minutes.

602
00:39:24,120 --> 00:39:25,160
What class?

603
00:39:25,160 --> 00:39:26,840
You've got 10 minutes. Write a new story.

604
00:39:26,840 --> 00:39:28,720
Otherwise, I'll beat you up.

605
00:39:28,720 --> 00:39:29,840
Wait a minute.

606
00:39:29,840 --> 00:39:30,880
Hurry up!

607
00:39:30,880 --> 00:39:32,680
Otherwise, I'll treat you to Children's Day.

608
00:39:34,800 --> 00:39:37,480
Assistant director! Move it!

609
00:39:37,480 --> 00:39:38,560
Hurry up, hurry up!

610
00:39:38,560 --> 00:39:39,840
All departments, hurry up!

611
00:39:39,840 --> 00:39:40,880
Get to work.

612
00:39:40,880 --> 00:39:42,760
Be quick.

613
00:39:42,760 --> 00:39:45,040
- This side too, be quick.
- Hurry up, hurry up.

614
00:39:45,040 --> 00:39:46,080
Faster.

615
00:39:46,080 --> 00:39:47,600
Everyone, move!

616
00:39:48,720 --> 00:39:50,320
Boss.

617
00:40:07,320 --> 00:40:08,960
- Boss.
- Assistant director.

618
00:40:08,960 --> 00:40:10,280
Here, here, here.

619
00:40:10,280 --> 00:40:12,520
Come on!

620
00:40:17,720 --> 00:40:19,640
Xiao Ma, help me check my clothes.

621
00:40:24,480 --> 00:40:25,480
Boss, Ma'am.

622
00:40:25,480 --> 00:40:26,560
Boss.

623
00:40:27,600 --> 00:40:28,880
- Boss.
- Boss.

624
00:40:28,880 --> 00:40:30,360
Boss.

625
00:40:30,360 --> 00:40:32,160
- Come over here.
- Come on over.

626
00:40:32,160 --> 00:40:33,920
Take Ma'am for makeup.

627
00:40:33,920 --> 00:40:36,280
This way. We're going to take makeup photos.

628
00:40:40,720 --> 00:40:41,720
Boss, this way.

629
00:40:41,720 --> 00:40:42,800
Please have a seat.

630
00:40:46,360 --> 00:40:47,680
Where's Liu Yi?

631
00:40:47,680 --> 00:40:50,200
Liu Yi is taking the screenwriter
to get inspiration.

632
00:40:50,200 --> 00:40:51,063
Write the script.

633
00:40:51,063 --> 00:40:54,200
I heard he's been hanging out at Lan Kai Feng.

634
00:40:54,200 --> 00:40:55,120
That's not true.

635
00:40:55,120 --> 00:40:58,320
I'm grateful that Liu Yi
takes me everywhere for inspiration.

636
00:40:58,320 --> 00:41:00,720
Otherwise, I couldn't have
written such a good story.

637
00:41:00,720 --> 00:41:02,040
That's nothing.

638
00:41:02,040 --> 00:41:04,400
Qing Long wants Liu Yi to make a movie.

639
00:41:04,400 --> 00:41:06,640
It has to be an Oscar-worthy one.

640
00:41:06,640 --> 00:41:07,680
Don't worry.

641
00:41:07,680 --> 00:41:09,640
If you need anything
in the future, just tell me.

642
00:41:09,640 --> 00:41:11,360
I will definitely help.

643
00:41:12,360 --> 00:41:15,000
Bro! What are you doing here?

644
00:41:15,960 --> 00:41:18,640
Dressed like Chow Yun Fat, too.

645
00:41:18,640 --> 00:41:20,720
I came to check on your Oscar-winning movie.

646
00:41:20,720 --> 00:41:22,320
How's the preparation going?

647
00:41:23,000 --> 00:41:24,840
Very simple.

648
00:41:28,480 --> 00:41:30,840
Xiao Man also wanted to go out for a walk, too.

649
00:41:39,120 --> 00:41:40,360
Sis.

650
00:41:41,160 --> 00:41:42,880
Don't scare her.

651
00:41:42,880 --> 00:41:45,160
The doctor said she can't be frightened now.

652
00:41:46,080 --> 00:41:47,720
What did the doctor say?

653
00:41:47,720 --> 00:41:49,560
Same as before.

654
00:41:49,560 --> 00:41:51,560
Her mind is getting more and more confused.

655
00:41:51,560 --> 00:41:53,480
Medication doesn't help.

656
00:41:53,480 --> 00:41:55,000
She often mistakes people.

657
00:41:55,000 --> 00:41:57,400
Sometimes, she doesn't even recognize me.

658
00:42:03,960 --> 00:42:05,560
Is he the screenwriter?

659
00:42:07,040 --> 00:42:08,080
Let me introduce him.

660
00:42:08,080 --> 00:42:09,600
A top student from HKU.

661
00:42:09,600 --> 00:42:11,760
Known as a drama-loving genius.

662
00:42:11,760 --> 00:42:13,880
He loves creating.

663
00:42:17,800 --> 00:42:19,960
A drama-loving genius.

664
00:42:19,960 --> 00:42:21,920
Talk about your script.

665
00:42:28,880 --> 00:42:30,480
Read it.

666
00:42:37,520 --> 00:42:39,160
A carefree and unruly gangster

667
00:42:39,160 --> 00:42:41,720
falls in love with a fallen, beautiful woman.

668
00:42:41,720 --> 00:42:45,080
After a romantic love
that moves heaven and earth...

669
00:42:46,160 --> 00:42:48,880
The woman is taken by a rival gang.

670
00:42:48,880 --> 00:42:51,480
The rival gang, who has long coveted her,

671
00:42:51,480 --> 00:42:52,920
seizes the opportunity
while the gangster is off guard

672
00:42:52,920 --> 00:42:54,920
and abducts her with overwhelming force,

673
00:42:54,920 --> 00:42:57,760
intending to use her
as leverage and humiliation.

674
00:42:57,760 --> 00:42:59,760
One man, dual blades, cuts down forty people.

675
00:42:59,760 --> 00:43:01,880
This plot sounds like...

676
00:43:01,880 --> 00:43:04,680
Liu Yi saving Qing Long.

677
00:43:04,680 --> 00:43:06,800
In the end, the gangster
and the beautiful woman

678
00:43:06,800 --> 00:43:08,800
live happily ever after.

679
00:43:15,680 --> 00:43:17,360
Hey! Why are you making things up?

680
00:43:17,360 --> 00:43:20,080
- Are you asking for trouble?
- I think it's great.

681
00:43:20,080 --> 00:43:21,720
Let's film it this way.

682
00:43:27,920 --> 00:43:29,760
After Xiao Man finishes the makeup photos,

683
00:43:29,760 --> 00:43:31,720
I'll pick you up for dinner at the villa.

684
00:43:31,720 --> 00:43:33,040
No, bro.

685
00:43:33,040 --> 00:43:35,160
His script is so...

686
00:43:36,000 --> 00:43:37,920
I've said it many times.

687
00:43:37,920 --> 00:43:40,880
If you wear a suit and tie,
make sure it's done properly.

688
00:43:42,480 --> 00:43:46,040
What? Did you expect me
to create something out of nothing?

689
00:43:46,040 --> 00:43:47,600
Rebellious kid.

690
00:43:47,600 --> 00:43:48,800
I'm leaving.

691
00:43:51,520 --> 00:43:53,000
Take care, bro.

692
00:44:08,120 --> 00:44:09,440
Xiao Ma.

693
00:44:10,320 --> 00:44:11,480
Take him down for a check.

694
00:44:11,480 --> 00:44:12,480
Got it.

695
00:44:12,480 --> 00:44:14,800
If there's no fracture,
keep him writing the script.

696
00:44:14,800 --> 00:44:15,960
Get up.

697
00:44:15,960 --> 00:44:17,960
- Let's go.
- Get up.

698
00:44:35,040 --> 00:44:38,000
Gangsters are all villains.

699
00:44:38,000 --> 00:44:41,160
Xia Liu Yi is a villain among villains.

700
00:44:48,560 --> 00:44:51,840
I've skipped class these past two days.

701
00:44:53,120 --> 00:44:55,240
I bet my scholarship is gone, too.

702
00:44:55,240 --> 00:44:57,480
Next year's tuition...

703
00:44:59,040 --> 00:45:01,960
Am I supposed to ask Dad for it?

704
00:45:01,960 --> 00:45:04,480
He works so hard...

705
00:45:04,480 --> 00:45:06,280
You wrote this?

706
00:45:07,880 --> 00:45:09,880
It's really well written.

707
00:45:17,360 --> 00:45:18,600
What's wrong?

708
00:45:18,600 --> 00:45:19,680
You okay?

709
00:45:19,680 --> 00:45:20,960
I'm fine.

710
00:45:23,880 --> 00:45:25,320
Who did this?

711
00:45:28,320 --> 00:45:31,400
It was Xia Liu Yi.

712
00:45:31,400 --> 00:45:32,880
Liu Yi's misbehaving again.

713
00:45:32,880 --> 00:45:35,200
- I'll go talk to him for you.
- No, no, no.

714
00:45:35,920 --> 00:45:37,920
Really, there's no need.

715
00:45:37,920 --> 00:45:39,680
You have to tell me.

716
00:45:40,480 --> 00:45:41,680
He's always like this.

717
00:45:41,680 --> 00:45:43,440
He can't make any friends.

718
00:45:58,040 --> 00:46:00,480
But don't blame him.

719
00:46:00,480 --> 00:46:02,720
He just has no one to play with.

720
00:46:10,480 --> 00:46:13,800
Back then, he was very pitiful.

721
00:46:13,800 --> 00:46:15,640
It was just him and me.

722
00:46:18,480 --> 00:46:20,800
Are you the female lead?

723
00:46:22,200 --> 00:46:24,120
Why aren't you filming?

724
00:46:25,040 --> 00:46:26,520
Filming?

725
00:46:32,000 --> 00:46:34,080
What's so good about filming?

726
00:46:35,000 --> 00:46:37,520
No matter how much I film,

727
00:46:37,520 --> 00:46:39,320
he won't watch it.

728
00:46:40,840 --> 00:46:42,320
I thought...

729
00:46:43,080 --> 00:46:44,840
I love him.

730
00:46:46,720 --> 00:46:48,640
And he loves me, too.

731
00:46:49,280 --> 00:46:51,720
That's supposed to be what love between us is.

732
00:46:54,360 --> 00:46:55,960
But...

733
00:47:02,200 --> 00:47:04,280
I heard you're a drama-loving genius.

734
00:47:04,280 --> 00:47:06,040
You're very good at writing about love, right?

735
00:47:12,400 --> 00:47:14,200
A drama-loving genius?

736
00:47:14,200 --> 00:47:16,280
He's just making it up.

737
00:47:20,920 --> 00:47:23,080
Then can you tell me...

738
00:47:23,080 --> 00:47:24,920
What is love?

739
00:47:27,600 --> 00:47:29,200
Love...

740
00:47:30,280 --> 00:47:31,520
Sis.

741
00:47:32,480 --> 00:47:34,240
Sis.

742
00:47:34,240 --> 00:47:36,280
Time for the photos. We're waiting for you.

743
00:47:37,200 --> 00:47:39,240
Sis.

744
00:47:39,240 --> 00:47:40,240
That's "Ma'am" for you.

745
00:47:40,240 --> 00:47:41,480
Liu Yi.

746
00:47:42,280 --> 00:47:43,720
You can't hit people.

747
00:47:43,720 --> 00:47:45,320
That's not good.

748
00:47:46,280 --> 00:47:47,480
Okay, fine.

749
00:47:47,480 --> 00:47:48,480
I was wrong.

750
00:47:48,480 --> 00:47:50,160
I won't do it again.

751
00:47:50,160 --> 00:47:52,280
You're the best behaved boy.

752
00:47:53,920 --> 00:47:55,760
All right. Let's go take photos.

753
00:47:55,760 --> 00:47:57,280
We've been waiting for you.

754
00:47:57,280 --> 00:47:58,840
Let's go.

755
00:48:00,960 --> 00:48:02,680
Then next time...

756
00:48:03,360 --> 00:48:05,160
Next time, tell me the answer.

757
00:48:09,480 --> 00:48:11,360
I'm watching you closely.

758
00:48:11,360 --> 00:48:13,200
Okay, fine.

759
00:48:13,200 --> 00:48:15,080
Let's go take the photos.

760
00:48:15,080 --> 00:48:16,640
Let's go.

761
00:48:27,045 --> 00:48:28,960
[Children's Day]

762
00:48:28,960 --> 00:48:31,000
I should go looking for inspiration.

763
00:48:53,520 --> 00:48:54,680
Just like a dog.

764
00:48:54,680 --> 00:48:56,400
Bark, bark, bark.

765
00:49:05,480 --> 00:49:07,200
What is love?

766
00:49:09,360 --> 00:49:11,320
Love is having someone

767
00:49:11,320 --> 00:49:13,480
willing to risk everything for you,

768
00:49:13,480 --> 00:49:16,240
even give up their life,

769
00:49:16,240 --> 00:49:18,680
just to save you from danger.

770
00:49:18,680 --> 00:49:19,960
Someone not afraid of getting hurt.

771
00:49:19,960 --> 00:49:21,400
Not afraid of pain.

772
00:49:21,400 --> 00:49:24,040
They might even risk their life.

773
00:49:24,040 --> 00:49:26,200
They'll stand up for you when you're helpless,

774
00:49:26,200 --> 00:49:28,160
and step forward bravely.

775
00:49:28,160 --> 00:49:31,880
They'll hold you tight
when you're on the brink of despair.

776
00:49:35,280 --> 00:49:36,680
Time to eat.

777
00:49:37,320 --> 00:49:38,880
Time to eat.

778
00:49:38,880 --> 00:49:39,880
Let's eat.

779
00:49:39,880 --> 00:49:41,960
Food's here!

780
00:49:41,960 --> 00:49:43,440
Time to eat, boss.

781
00:49:44,760 --> 00:49:46,600
Eat first, then play.

782
00:49:46,600 --> 00:49:47,840
- Come eat.
- Time to eat.

783
00:49:47,840 --> 00:49:50,000
Time to eat.

784
00:49:50,000 --> 00:49:51,360
Time to eat!

785
00:50:01,840 --> 00:50:03,000
He Chu San.

786
00:50:03,000 --> 00:50:05,200
- Come eat, now.
- Okay, got it.

787
00:50:15,400 --> 00:50:22,160
Boss!

788
00:50:22,160 --> 00:50:23,400
Are you okay?

789
00:50:33,480 --> 00:50:35,400
If one day,

790
00:50:35,400 --> 00:50:39,160
someone like this appears in your life,

791
00:50:39,160 --> 00:50:41,160
don't hesitate for a second.

792
00:50:41,160 --> 00:50:43,280
Don't run away.

793
00:50:43,280 --> 00:50:44,960
Use all your strength.

794
00:50:44,960 --> 00:50:46,720
Hold onto them tightly.

795
00:50:49,720 --> 00:50:51,400
Are you okay?

796
00:50:51,400 --> 00:50:52,640
I'm fine.

797
00:50:55,855 --> 00:50:57,240
Boss, how are you?

798
00:50:57,240 --> 00:50:58,560
Boss, are you okay?

799
00:51:01,480 --> 00:51:02,800
How about you?

800
00:51:02,800 --> 00:51:03,800
Are you hurt?

801
00:51:03,800 --> 00:51:07,400
Because their eyes will tell you one thing.

802
00:51:07,400 --> 00:51:08,960
"I love you."

803
00:51:30,640 --> 00:51:32,920
Boss, I'll shut them up.

804
00:51:32,920 --> 00:51:34,200
Don't bother.

805
00:51:37,800 --> 00:51:39,200
This is a happy moment.
